{
  "stem": "24409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But after I call out as he counted and say after two, or maybe even before two, but before three, I told him, I have some information which you very much would like to have, and which is much more important, probably, than the name of this man.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, tell me your swindles, your swindling scheme.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him that we had organized transports to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, put it down in writing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then after, a short time later, he knew that we had organized boycotts in Germany, apparently, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took [INAUDIBLE] and threw it out, and me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know whether there was somebody else in this police vehicle where you transport arrested people to the office of the Revisionist organization.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, we had loads of correspondence with, regarding, the boycott of German goods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Turi [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Deutsche ?] has put them all in a heap in front of the door, on the side, on the wall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They searched the office and didn't look at this bunch there in front of the wall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They searched the office only very superficially.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they sent us home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I then composed the very thoughtful article, the memorandum, which I give gave to Eichmann, which I have very recently made a translation because the original is hardly readable.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Original was with The Nazis, but I had carbon copies of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the carbon copies, in the course of 50 years, you didn't see too much of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I had a carbon copy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I gave one carbon copy, I believe, to the museum, to the Holocaust Museum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I had the carbon copy, which I could make out, because I knew what it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
